data.description: Cute home in the heart of West! This newly renovated home has been updated yet still shines with 1930s charm. This 1,146 sq ft home sits on a shaded 1/4 of an acre and is completely fenced. It also has a variety of crops, including peach trees, plum trees, and corn! Inside you will find two spacious bedrooms and a large bathroom with a double vanity. Fresh window panes have been installed, and seller is willing to replace AC system once house goes under contract! The kitchen has granite counters and a beautiful tile backsplash. The indoor laundry room has shiplap accents with a new tile floor. Come check out this adorable home today! Ask about the 2.875% assumable interest rate!
